title: Stef Bos - De Nachtwaker (Dutch Treat ^B063 HQ VBR MP3)
description:
Talking about the Dutch language. Stef Bos deserves rewarding. Dutch is a hard language to sing. Stef - as no other (maybe Johan Verminnen) - succeeds in using simple Dutch to take you towards a level in which you are willing to accept things as they are. Showing some truth about the nature of the Dutch language (and consciousness).
 
Its hard to catch Stef within one playlist. A lot depends on listening and two hours is a long time and too many candidates to end up in the best 30 tracks. With every decision I thought `What would Stef do`. So I ended up with this 32 tracks list. And really, I myself am really proud to hear Stef like this.... Enjoy,
